{"content": "I need to multiply 404 \u00d7 613 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 404\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 0 + 4\u00d71 = 324 + 0 + 4 = 328\u2081\u2080\n- 613\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 486 + 9 + 3 = 498\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 328 \u00d7 498 = 163,344\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 163344 \u00f7 9 = 18149 r 3\n- 18149 \u00f7 9 = 2016 r 5\n- 2016 \u00f7 9 = 224 r 0\n- 224 \u00f7 9 = 24 r 8\n- 24 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 6\n- 2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: **268053\u2089**\n\n268053", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 342}